Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: bump
Version: 0.2.0
Summary: Bumps package version numbers
Home-page: https://github.com/marksteve/bump
Author: Mark Steve Samson
Author-email: hello@marksteve.com
License: MIT
Description: bump
        ====
        
        Bumps package version numbers
        
        Usage:
        ------
        
        ::
        
            $ bump setup.py
            1.0.2 => 1.0.3
            Is this ok? y/n y
            Updated setup.py
        
            $ bump setup.py -M
            1.0.2 => 2.0.0
            Is this ok? y/n y
            Updated setup.py
        
            $ bump setup.py -m
            2.0.0 => 2.1.0
            Is this ok? y/n y
            Updated setup.py
        
Keywords: bump increment package version
